          "reviewBody": "Sarcastic post but serious details.\n\nCame to know about a sport day event conducted and the chief guest fainted due to Sun/heat. Poor mgmt on many things. Students and parents were treated based on the mood swing of staffs and teachers.\n\nDear staffs, teachers and the chief guest,\nGet well soon..!",
