            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst experience never had in any school... 😡\nVery very poor management\nEnglish communication worst to the core zero\nEspecially admins tey r very rude.. No Patience... Tey never answer for parents.. Tey ll never listen to parents queries 😡\n\nAcademic wise primary teaching is zero..\nGot tc nd changed my child school...\n\nIf your planning to put ur kids here a big noooo...",
          "publisher": {
