          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "3 children from my family study here.\nIt’s a very good CBSE school in this locality! Compared to other schools, fees are nominal and teachers are really kind and flexible. Well organised events and activities for kindergarten and higher classes too!\n\nI would highly recommend young parents for their kids. I’m very satisfied with teachers and the other staff who help children.\n\nOffice staff r bit rude and strict but I find it okay as it’s tough to handle so many of them at a time.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
