            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Dance Rj"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-02-28",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I’m not sure of the good reviews here - probably it’s bcoz of early stage where chetpet Maharishi school teachers were teaching.\n\nCurrent situation as of 2023.\n\nPros :\nExtra curricular activities is good.\nGood location\nNew building\nCost is ok\n\nCons\nVery very poor management.\n\nStaffs are mostly parents of the students studying. No teaching experience.\n\nEnglish communication is ZERO.\n\nTeachers are mostly like next door aunties. You don’t get feel like they are teachers.\n\nBig communication gap between school and parents. There will be no prior communications.\nParents app is there but is not properly used .\n\nTeachers treat students very badly - if asked questions - there won’t be proper reply but student will be punished…\n\nIf you planning to put your ward in this school - you must have more patience and tolerance.",
